With <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">China</ENAMEX> 's renovation of <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC">the Grand Canal</ENAMEX> , its watercourse conditions have been greatly improved .
Many enterprises have successively taken a fancy for <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC">this " Golden Waterway "</ENAMEX> and are now actively investing in building factories .
