The large - scale renovation of <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC">the Grand Canal</ENAMEX> has improved the investment environment of the cities and counties along the canal , has attracted foreign investment with its benefit of advantageous water transportation , and has promoted the development of an export - oriented economy .
